57	/**
58	 * Walk a Claude Code transcript jsonl and return assistant-turn usage entries.
59	 *
60	 * Each returned entry: { messageId, model, usage, timestamp, turnIndex }
61	 * - `messageId` from `message.id` (stable per assistant turn)
62	 * - `model` from `message.model`
